    "pronunciationCoaching": "**Target Phrase:** ANAC123, Speed Nine Zero Knots\n\n**Pronunciation:** AY-nak WUN TOO THREE, SPEED NYN ZE-ro NOTS\n\n**Word Stress**\n\n- Indicated → IN-dih-kay-tid\n- Airspeed → AIR-speed\n- Knots → NOTS\n- Maintain → mayn-TAYN\n\nPractice:\n\nSay indicated airspeed... speed nine zero knots.\n\nTogether:\n\nANAC123, speed nine zero knots. ANAC123, unable one two zero knots, maintaining nine five.",
