    "meaningEn": "First Officer is the licensed co-pilot who serves as second-in-command on a multi-crew aircraft, performing pilot flying or pilot monitoring duties as assigned and assuming command if the captain becomes incapacitated.",
    "meaningPt": "Primeiro oficial / First Officer / Copiloto.\n\nCopiloto licenciado que atua como segundo em comando em aeronave multi-crew, desempenhando funções de piloto voando ou piloto monitorando conforme designado e assumindo o comando se o capitão ficar incapacitado.",
    "whenUsed": "When operating as or referring to a first officer, the crew should:",
