    "memoryTrick": "**FO** — **F**ly if required, **O**wn the monitoring role; in takeover: **F**irst officer assuming control, **O**btain vectors and medical help.",
    "operationalMeaning": "When operating as or referring to a first officer, the crew should:\n\nFirst officer communications commonly include:",
