    "pronunciationCoaching": "**Target Phrase:** Sandstorm Over the Field, Request Divert\n\n**Pronunciation:** SAND-storm OH-ver thuh FEELD, reh-KWEST di-VERT\n\n**Word Stress**\n\n- Sandstorm → SAND-storm\n- Field → FEELD\n- Divert → di-VERT\n- Visibility → viz-uh-BIL-ih-tee\n\nPractice:\n\nSandstorm over the field... request divert...\n\nTogether:\n\nANAC123, sandstorm over the field, unable approach, request divert.",
