    "pronunciationCoaching": "**Target Phrase:** Dust Storm Over the Field, Request Divert\n\n**Pronunciation:** DUST STORM OH-ver thuh FEELD, reh-KWEST di-VERT\n\n**Word Stress**\n\n- Dust → DUST\n- Storm → STORM\n- Divert → di-VERT\n- Visibility → viz-uh-BIL-ih-tee\n\nPractice:\n\nDust storm... over the field... request divert...\n\nTogether:\n\nANAC123, dust storm over the field, unable approach, request divert.",
