    "pronunciationCoaching": "**Target Phrase:** Main Gearbox Chip Detector, Request Priority Landing\n\n**Pronunciation:** MAYN GEAR-boks CHIP dee-TEK-ter, reh-KWEST pry-OR-ih-tee LAN-ding\n\n**Word Stress**\n\n- Gearbox → GEAR-boks\n- Chip → CHIP\n- Detector → dee-TEK-ter (stress on second)\n- Priority → pry-OR-ih-tee\n\nPractice:\n\nMain gearbox chip detector... request priority landing.\n\nTogether:\n\nMain gearbox chip detector, reducing power, request priority landing.",
