    "brazilianMistakes": "- ❌ Continuing the full mission after a significant overtorque with no report.  \n  ✔ Land for inspection per AFM and company criteria.\n\n- ❌ Reducing collective so abruptly that Nr exceeds limits.  \n  ✔ Reduce smoothly while protecting rotor RPM.\n\n- ❌ Saying \"power exceedance\" without torque.  \n  ✔ State engine overtorque clearly.\n\n- ❌ Accepting a high-power departure or go-around after overtorque.  \n  ✔ Plan a conservative approach; avoid unnecessary high torque.",
    "pronunciationCoaching": "**Target Phrase:** Engine Overtorque, Request Priority Landing\n\n**Pronunciation:** EN-jin OH-ver-tork, reh-KWEST pry-OR-ih-tee LAN-ding\n\n**Word Stress**\n\n- Engine → EN-jin\n- Overtorque → OH-ver-tork (stress on first)\n- Priority → pry-OR-ih-tee\n- Landing → LAN-ding\n\nPractice:\n\nEngine overtorque... request priority landing.\n\nTogether:\n\nEngine overtorque, reducing power, request priority landing.",
