    "pronunciationCoaching": "**Target Phrase:** Burning Odour in Cabin, No Visible Fire, Priority Landing\n\n**Pronunciation:** BUR-ning OH-der in CAB-in, noh VIZ-uh-bul FYR, pry-OR-ih-tee LAN-ding\n\n**Word Stress**\n\n- Burning → BUR-ning\n- Odour → OH-der\n- Visible → VIZ-uh-bul\n- Priority → pry-OR-ih-tee\n\nPractice:\n\nBurning odour... no visible fire... request priority landing.\n\nTogether:\n\nBurning odour in cabin, no visible fire, request priority landing.",
